<concept id="Prerequisites">
    <title>Prerequisites</title>
    <conbody>
        <section>
            <title>OQS Permissions</title>
            <p>User authentication is not required to perform the following actions:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>View the Pods radiator page.</li>
              <li>View the Pods list page.</li>
              <li>View the Pods historical-logs list page.</li>

              <li>View individual Pods information pages.</li>
              <li>View individual Pods log pages.</li>

              <li>View the Deployments historical-logs list page.</li>
              <li>View individual Deployments log pages.</li>
            </ul>
            <p>The following actions, however, do require User authentication:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Create Pods</li>
              <li>Update Pods (Admin users only)</li>
              <li>Delete Pods (Admin users only)</li>
              <li>Update Deployment Status (Admin users only)</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
    </conbody>
</concept>
